onale", "source_file": "docs/plan/faza-4.5.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_plan_faza_4_5_d62", "label": "D62 \u2014 parseHost przyjmuje domen\u0119 bazow\u0105 parametrem, nie czyta env; rationale: vitest.config.ts zabrania testom si\u0119ga\u0107 do @/lib/env/server", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/plan/faza-4.5.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_plan_faza_4_5_d63", "label": "D63 \u2014 Subdomeny w E2E z uniqueSubdomain, nie z uniqueId; rationale: uniqueId \u0142\u0105czy podkre\u015blnikami niedopuszczalnymi w SUBDOMAIN_PATTERN, host parsuje si\u0119 jako foreign", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/plan/faza-4.5.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_plan_faza_4_5_d64", "label": "D64 \u2014 Bramka landingu w [locale]/page.tsx, nie w catch-allu; rationale: catch-all nie \u0142apie \u015bcie\u017cki pustej", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/plan/faza-4.5.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_plan_faza_4_5_d65", "label": "D65 \u2014 Fixture sharedRequest (context.request) obok istniej\u0105cego request; rationale: playwright.request.newContext() ma w\u0142asny s\u0142oik cookies", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/plan/faza-4.5.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_plan_faza_4_5_d66", "label": "D66 \u2014 Bramka landingu pyta servedSubdomain(), nie servedOrganization(); rationale: drugi warunek zwraca null r\u00f3wnie\u017c dla nieistniej\u0105cej akademii, wi\u0119c marketing serwowa\u0142by si\u0119 pod dowoln\u0105 subdomen\u0105", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/plan/faza-4